1) Commands are actually files containing programs, often written in C. How will you find out in which directory does  the file corresponding to the man command resides?
ANS)
    which man
    This will return the path to the executable file associated with the man command.

2) How will you find out what is the use of the ps command.
ANS)
    man ps
    After running this command, you will see the manual page for the ps command, which provides detailed information on how to use it, the available options, and examples of common usage.